《'''阿凡達'''》（{{lang-en|''Avatar''}}{{notetag|「Avatar」是[[英語|英語]]向[[梵語|梵語]]借字，有「[[化身_(印度教)|化身]]」的意思。}}）是一部[[2009年電影|2009年]]上映的[[美國|美國]]<ref>{{cite news |author=French, Philip|title=Avatar was the year's real milestone, never mind the results|date=2010-03-14|work=The Observer|location=UK |url = https://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/mar/14/avatar-kathryn-bigelow-hollywood-history |accessdate = 2010-03-29| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100317150833/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2010/mar/14/avatar-kathryn-bigelow-hollywood-history| archivedate=March 17, 2010 <!--DASHBot-->| deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Rich|last=Johnston|title=Review: AVATAR – The Most Expensive American Film Ever ... And Possibly The Most Anti-American One Too.|date=2009-12-11|publisher=[[Bleeding_Cool|Bleeding Cool]]|url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2009/12/11/review-avatar-the-most-expensive-american-film-ever-and-the-most-anti-american-one-too/|accessdate=2010-03-29|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68FxVKw1Y?url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2009/12/11/review-avatar-the-most-expensive-american-film-ever-and-the-most-anti-american-one-too/|archive-date=2012-06-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[史詩|史詩式]][[科幻電影|科幻電影]]，為[[阿凡達系列電影|阿凡達系列]]的第一部電影。由[[詹姆斯·卡麥隆|詹姆斯·卡麥隆]]撰寫劇本並執導，主要演員有[[山姆·沃辛頓|山姆·沃辛頓]]、[[佐伊·索爾達娜|柔伊·沙達納]]、[[雪歌妮·薇佛|雪歌妮·薇佛]]、[[米歇爾·羅德里格茲|蜜雪兒·羅德里奎茲]]和[[斯蒂芬·朗_(演員)|史帝芬·朗]]。 

電影設定於2154年，當時人類正在[[南門二|南門二]]恆星系生態茂盛的潘朵拉[[衛星_(天體)|衛星]]上開採珍稀礦產[[難得素|難得素]]。<ref name="Horwitz2009" /> 採礦殖民地的擴張威脅到了當地部落[[纳美人|纳美人]]的生存：納美人是土生土長於潘多拉星球上的有[[感知|感知]]智慧能力的[[類人|類人]][[種族|種族]]。「阿凡達」指的是經過[[基因工程|基因改造]]而能為部分人類所控制的納美人身體，人類使用他們來同潘朵拉星上的原住民展開交流<ref name="Time" />。 

阿凡達的開發始於1994年，卡梅隆當時為這部電影撰寫了80頁的[[劇本論述|劇本論述]]<ref name="QA">{{cite news | author=Jeff Jensen | url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20007998,00.html | title=Great Expectations | work=[[娛樂週刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | publisher=[[時代華納|Time Warner]] | date=2007-01-10 | accessdate=2010-02-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070124101323/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20007998%2C00.html | archive-date=2007-01-24 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。柯麥隆原計劃在1997年的《[[鐵達尼號_(1997年電影)|鐵達尼號]]》攝製完成後就開始製作這部電影，並打算在1999年上映<ref name="autogenerated2">{{cite news | author= | url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=888&dat=19960812&id=8rsMAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Al8DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6553,2562816 | title=Synthetic actors to star in ''Avatar'' | work=St. Petersburg Times | publisher=Times Publishing Company | date=1996-08-12 | accessdate=2010-02-14}}</ref>，但最終未能如愿。柯麥隆解釋說，當時的技術手段還不足以表現出他想像的電影場景。<ref name="autogenerated1996">{{cite news | author=Judy Hevrdejs | coauthors=Mike Conklin | url= | title=Channel 2 has Monday morning team in place | work=Chicago Tribune | date=1996-08-09 | accessdate=2010-02-14 }}</ref>為電影中的[[外星生命|外星人]]創造[[納美語|語言]]的工作開始於2005年夏天，柯麥隆也在2006年初開始發展[[劇本|劇本]]及其[[阿凡達的虛構世界|虛構世界]]。<ref name='USCMarshall'>{{cite web |url=http://www.marshall.usc.edu/news/all-articles/crafting-an-alien.htm |title=Crafting an Alien Language, Hollywood-Style: Professor's Work to Hit the Big Screen in Upcoming Blockbuster Avatar |accessdate=2010-02-14 |work=USC Marshall |publisher=University of Southern California Marshall School of Business |archive-date=2010-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101126043448/http://www.marshall.usc.edu/news/all-articles/crafting-an-alien.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="radionz1">{{Cite episode| title = Avatar Language| series = Nine to Noon| airdate = 2009-12-15| url = http://www.radionz.co.nz/audio/national/ntn/2009/12/15/avatar_language| access-date = 2010-02-14| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924084247/http://www.radionz.co.nz/audio/national/ntn/2009/12/15/avatar_language| archive-date = 2015-09-24| dead-url = no}}</ref>

官方公佈的《阿凡達》製作費為2.37億[[美元|美元]]<ref name="Patten (2009)" />。其餘的估計則認為[[電影製作|電影製作]]大概花費了2.8至3.1億美元，另外投入1.5億美元到市場的宣傳營銷上<ref name="latimes budget">{{cite web | url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2009/12/could-avatar-hit-1-billion.html | title=Could 'Avatar' hit $1 billion? | work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | publisher=Tribune Company | author=Fritz, Ben | date=2009-12-20 | accessdate=2010-02-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091222081117/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/entertainmentnewsbuzz/2009/12/could-avatar-hit-1-billion.html | archive-date=2009-12-22 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="vanityfair" /><ref name="www.nytimes.com">{{cite news|first=Brooks|last=Barnes|title='Avatar' Is No. 1 but Without a Record|work=[[紐約時報|The New York Times]]|publisher=The New York Times Company|date=2009-12-20|accessdate=2010-02-14|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/12/21/movies/21box.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111113023114/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/12/21/movies/21box.html|archive-date=2011-11-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在發行上，這部電影不僅使用了傳統的[[維度|2D]][[電影放映機|放映]]格式，還使用了包括[[RealD_戲院|RealD 3D]]、[[杜比数字|Dolby 3D]]、[[XpanD_3D|XpanD 3D]]和[[IMAX#IMAX_3D|IMAX 3D]]在內的多種[[3D電影|3D]]格式，乃至[[4D電影|4D]]格式<ref name=4-D>{{cite web | author=Han Sunhee | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118014803.html?categoryid=2526&cs=1 | title='Avatar' goes 4D in Korea | date=2010-02-05 | accessdate=2010-02-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100210010141/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118014803.html?categoryid=2526&cs=1 | archive-date=2010-02-10 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。因為在3D視野和[[立體觀察|立体视觉]]製片上有著諸多創新，這部電影被譽為電影製片技術上的一大突破<ref>{{cite web |url=http://newsblaze.com/story/2009102916560100002.pnw/topstory.html |title=James Cameron's 'Avatar' Film to Feature Vocals From Singer Lisbeth Scott |publisher=Newsblaze.com |date= |accessdate=2010-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091206050359/http://newsblaze.com/story/2009102916560100002.pnw/topstory.html |archive-date=2009-12-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。因為這部電影，爾後所有好萊塢動作片都使用了3D拍攝技術，之後，3D放映版本也開始遍及全世界幾乎所有的首輪戲院。

2009年12月10日，《阿凡達》在[[倫敦|倫敦]]舉行了[[預映|預映]]，12月16日開始全球上映，北美地區則在12月18日上映。上映後，電影好評如潮，實現了商業成功<ref name='D'>{{cite news | first=Anthony | last=D'Alessandro | coauthors= | authorlink= | title='Avatar' takes $27 million in its first day | date=2009-12-19 | publisher=Reed Business Information | url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118012989.html?categoryid=3762&cs=1 | work=[[綜藝|Variety]] | pages= | accessdate=2010-02-14 | language= | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68FxZvo2f?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118012989?refCatId=3762 | archive-date=2012-06-08 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="www.comingsoon.net">{{cite web|first=Edward|last=Douglas|title=Avatar Soars Despite Heavy Snowstorms|work=ComingSoon.net|publisher=CraveOnline|date=2009-12-21|accessdate=2010-02-14|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=61739|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68FxagzwR?url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=61739|archive-date=2012-06-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="www.reuters.com">{{cite web|author=Reporting by Dean Goodman; editing by Anthony Boadle|title="Avatar" leads box office, despite blizzard|work=[[路透社|Reuters]]|publisher=Thomson Reuters|date=2009-12-20|accessdate=2010-02-14|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSN2021595320091220?type=marketsNews|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100126223705/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSN2021595320091220?type=marketsNews|archive-date=2010-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在上映期間，這部電影打破了不少票房記錄，成為了有史以來北美（不考慮通貨膨脹）乃至全球[[最高電影票房收入列表|票房收入最高的電影]]，超過了保持這一紀錄12年之久的《鐵達尼號》<ref>{{cite web|first=|last=|title=All Time Worldwide Box Office Grosses|publisher=Box Office Mojo|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/|accessdate=2010-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100102025933/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/world/|archive-date=2010-01-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此紀錄維持了近10年之久，於2019年7月20日被《[[復仇者聯盟：終局之戰|復仇者聯盟：終局之戰]]》所超越<ref>{{cite news |author1=許世穎 |title=號外！《復仇者4》超車《阿凡達》 登頂影史之冠 |url=https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2859260 |work=[[自由時報|自由時報]] |date=2019-07-21 |access-date=2019-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721145717/https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2859260 |archive-date=2019-07-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，又在2021年3月中国重映后重夺票房榜冠军<ref>{{cite web |last1=Tartaglione |first1=Nancy |title=‘Avatar’ Overtakes ‘Avengers: Endgame’ As All-Time Highest-Grossing Film At Global Box Office; China Reissue Growing |url=https://deadline.com/2021/03/avatar-overtakes-avengers-endgame-highest-grossing-film-all-time-worldwide-box-office-china-james-cameron-disney-1234713788/ |website=Deadline |accessdate=2021-03-13 |date=2021-03-13}}</ref>。《阿凡達》還是首部票房收入超過20億美元的電影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory?id=9711561|title='Avatar' Wins Box Office, Nears Domestic Record|accessdate=2010-02-14|publisher=ABC News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100203052551/http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/wireStory?id=9711561|archive-date=2010-02-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。計入[[通貨膨脹|通貨膨脹]]後仍然是史上第二高的電影（相當於2019年價值的$3,273,000,000），僅次於[[亂世佳人|亂世佳人]]（相當於2019年價值的$3,728,000,000）<ref name="Guinness 2015">{{cite book |title=Guinness World Records |edition=2015 |year=2014 |volume=60 |isbn=9781908843708 |pages=160–161|last1=Records |first1=Guinness World }}</ref>。

