作曲家[[詹姆斯·霍納|詹姆斯·霍納]]為這部電影配樂，這是他繼《[[異形2|異形2]]》與《[[鐵達尼號_(1997年電影)|鐵達尼號]]》後第三次與柯麥隆合作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.filmmusicweekly.com/issues/FM_Weekly_061907.pdf|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071129050902/http://www.filmmusicweekly.com/issues/FM_Weekly_061907.pdf|archivedate=2007-11-29|title=Fox confirms Horner on Cameron's 'Avatar'|accessdate=2010-02-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2008年3月，霍納和一支小型合唱團合作，錄製了納美語演唱的部分配樂。<ref>{{cite news | author = Dorey, Jim | title = Na'vi Alien Language Incorporated In 'Avatar' Music Soundtrack | work = MarketSaw Blog | date = 2008-04-02 | url = http://marketsaw.blogspot.com/2008/04/navi-alien-language-incorporated-in.html | accessdate = 2010-02-25 | archivedate = 2010-01-25 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5n2I8pPmL?url=http://marketsaw.blogspot.com/2008/04/navi-alien-language-incorporated-in.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>霍納還同[[民族音樂學|民族音樂學家]]萬達·布賴恩特（{{small|Bryant}}）合作，為該外星種族創造[[音樂|音樂]][[文化|文化]]。<ref>{{cite news | author = Lucas, Ann | title = Alumni News | publisher = UCLA Department of Ethnomusicology | date = 2007年秋 | url = http://www.ethnomusic.ucla.edu/publications/newsletters/newsletterfall07.pdf | accessdate = 2010-02-25 | format = PDF | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/5mpzpE6Od?url=http://www.ethnomusic.ucla.edu/publications/newsletters/newsletterfall07.pdf | archive-date = 2010-01-17 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>第一次配樂演奏計劃在2009年春展開。<ref>{{cite news | author = Carlsson, Mikael | title = Top-10 Most Anticipated Scores of 2009 | work = Upcoming Film Scores | publisher = IMDb News | date = 2009-01-03 | url = http://www.imdb.com/news/ni0640218/l | accessdate = 2010-02-25 | archivedate = 2010-01-25 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5n2HcblaU?url=http://www.imdb.com/news/ni0640218/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>在製作期間，霍納向柯麥隆保證說他不會在此期間參與《阿凡達》以外的任何計劃；有報導稱霍納每天早晨4點就開始工作，一直持續到晚上10點。霍納在一次採訪中談到：「《阿凡達》是我做過的最難的電影，也是我接到的最大的工作。<ref>{{cite news | author = Owen Vaughan | title = James Horner: 'Scoring Avatar has been the most difficult job I've done' done | work =  | publisher = Times Online | date = 2009-11-30 | url = http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article6936869.ece | accessdate = 2010-02-25 | quote = ''Avatar'' has been the most difficult film I have worked on and the biggest job I have undertaken. | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110615070325/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article6936869.ece | archive-date = 2011-06-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>霍納譜寫的配樂是由兩段風格迥異的配樂合成的：他首先創作了一首反映納美人發聲方式的配樂，然後再將其與另一首「傳統的」配樂結合。<ref name="makingofavatar" />電影的主題曲{{《}}[[我看見你_(阿凡達主題曲)|我看見你]]{{》}}由英國歌手[[利昂娜·劉易斯|利昂娜·劉易斯]]演唱。2009年12月15日，片方在[[MySpace|MySpace]]上公開了由{{link-en|傑克·納瓦|Jake Nava}}導演的一段伴奏片段。<ref>{{cite news | author = Fukushima, Glenn | title = Atlantic Unveils "AVATAR: MUSIC FROM THE MOTION PICTURE"; Official Companion Album to James Cameron's Upcoming Epic Adventure Features Music Composed & Conducted by Oscar®-Winner James Horner, Plus "I See You (Theme From Avatar)," Performed by Leona Lewis | publisher = marketwire | date = 2009-11-16 | url = http://www.marketwire.com/press-release/Atlantic-Records-1076978.html | accessdate = 2010-02-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091119133856/http://www.marketwire.com/press-release/Atlantic-Records-1076978.html | archive-date = 2009-11-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

