ive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618031002/http://www.comic-con.org/cci2009/cci09_prog_thu.php |archive-date=2013-06-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和24日<ref name="Comic-Con">{{cite web |url=http://www.comic-con.org/cci2009/cci09_prog_fri.php |title=Programming for Friday, July 24th |publisher=San Diego Comic-Con International |format=php |accessdate=2010-02-25 |date=2009-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130426053949/http://www.comic-con.org/cci2009/cci09_prog_fri.php |archive-date=2013-04-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>發言。柯麥隆在動漫大會的阿凡達討論會上宣佈說，8月21日將成為「阿凡達日」<ref>原文：「Avatar Day」．</ref>。《阿凡達》的預告片將在這一天以影院支持的所有格式發佈；而電影的官方遊戲預告片和系列玩具也會在同一天揭曉。<ref>{{cite news|title=Official 'Avatar Day' Press Release|work=SciFiScoop.com|date=2009-07-23|url=http://www.scifiscoop.com/news/official-avatar-day-press-release/|accessdate=2010-02-25|archivedate=2010-01-25|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5n2GwTz8c?url=http://www.scifiscoop.com/news/official-avatar-day-press-release/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

